## ğŸ“ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.8+  
- OpenAI API key  
- Supabase project  
- Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

git clone https://github.com/your-username/surveygpt-ai.git
cd surveygpt-ai
cp .env.example .env  # Fill in your environment variables
streamlit run app.py


